<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style>
        .container{
            margin:100px auto;
            padding:30px;
            width:750px;
            height:420px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border:10px solid lightskyblue;
        }
        .head{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-family: 仿宋;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content{
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding:50px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content div{
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content div span{
            font-size: 18px;
            font-family: 微软雅黑;
            color: #4C4C4C;
        }
        .content div input{
            padding-left: 10px;
            width:250px;
            height:30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .content div:nth-child(2){
            margin-left: -15px;
        }
        .content div:nth-child(4)>input{
            cursor: pointer;
            width:110px;
            height: 40px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid lightgreen;
            background: lightgreen;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="head">
        欢迎来到邮件系统！
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <form action="/users" method="post">
            <div><span>邮箱：</span><input type="text" name='address' placeholder="请输入邮箱地址"></div>
            <div><span>用户名：</span><input type="text" name='username' placeholder="请输入用户名"></div>
            <div><span>密码：</span><input type="password" name='password' placeholder="请输入密码"></div>
            <div><input type="submit" value  ="注册"></div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>